Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 才不是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 话说你胸部绝对变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得有点恶心啦 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死去死去死去死 去死去死去死去死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要再把劣质的基因传下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发了情的淫兽们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死 去死 去死…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:35.72,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建筑工：原文ビルビルダー，估计\N出自口袋妖怪中的某个生物名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?这个是「建筑工」吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 女人真是笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～但是很像哦 那只长很多嘴的那么肥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥就算的话 珠算补习班里的那老头也是建筑工…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…可是啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的野兽 非常地 凶猛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也要吃 咸拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鸡蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间要吃蛋花汤 蛋花汤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋…要凝固了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鸡蛋搅开啦 搅开 搅开…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么啊 拉面?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:33.53,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是叔叔! 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 仁太也给我做一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:42.89,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哎? 为什么给叔叔做就不给芽间做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那见啥都说可爱的习惯该改改了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.06,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}叔叔之前也有说芽间的墓很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 但这是个好词啊 哪里都能用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不会用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋要什么样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个荷包蛋 不要散咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:54.24,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 连叔叔也是!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏心 偏心 偏心大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视电视…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 猫咪好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸的表现也没有反常 看来果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡椒胡椒胡椒胡椒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筷子在哪儿 筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你怎么了 在家里中暑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱但是…不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的夏天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然还是仁碳的最大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 鹤见子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:11.53,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\frz269.5\pos(1187,430)}仁太：
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:11.53,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\frz269.5\pos(1139,464)}我去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:11.53,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\frz269.5\pos(1090,479)}你好好休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…怎么了这是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实是病了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定是因为一直顶着的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有心理的阴影…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为夏天的炎热成了形…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…还有青春期的性冲动也一起来了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作是我的压力造成你实体化出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么到现在才出现?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是以成长后的姿态出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…就算你这么问…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 也许…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能芽间是想来实现愿望的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望? 什么愿望?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那个也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望都不知道是什么怎么实现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…但是 我就感觉是想来实现愿望的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…到底是什么愿望呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口水飞出来了 真讨厌!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏障!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}这可是无敌的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙就是夏天的猛兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.97,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}这下芽间无敌了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的压力 我的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先把你说的愿望想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对啊 对啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是必须要大家一起才能实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 大家是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…有人在敲门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被别人看到你怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了给我乖乖地…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.98,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是安鸣啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 安 安城…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 冷静…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没激动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀怎么好像很沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…看不见芽间…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师让我转交你的暑假作业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假…我说 已经只剩两天…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不像宿海 我有很多事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你找个地方扔了不就行了 这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正那种白痴高中 我也没动力去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来不来无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你太不像话了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳是白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不拜托安鸣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「拜托了 让我们一起实现愿望吧 安鸣~」这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管她…叫安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城 鸣子 要叫就叫这两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么? 安鸣就是安鸣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对大家很温柔 会拿来很多游戏和漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙已经 不是那时候的安鸣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拜托那个臭娘们 她也不可能会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「臭娘们」?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是蠢女人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 那家伙已经不是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…说安鸣坏话的仁碳 我讨厌!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 再去一次安鸣那儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拜托她吧 仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你那个愿望说给安城听 你就会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是安城 一切都和那时候不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁碳 还没好?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子和眼镜?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 买东西去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有拉面的葱粘着哦 在牙齿上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 安鸣家不是这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便散步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里以前是BomBom吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成WcDonald了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 不过芽间更喜欢炸肉饼面包…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一个学校的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:09.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:13.65,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有外星人出来 和有个使双截棍的女的在学校打的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:15.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 那是什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 我只是被两个大妈搞坏了心情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不会在意我这种人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城不是也说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人 怎么都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花～折下来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的味道～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是没变啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然的吧 她只是我的幻觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现愿望…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 这肯定是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对芽间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干啥 很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 小芽间她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:03.97,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,184)}第一集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:03.97,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(328,356)}超和平Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去小仁家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲门!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 刚才没敲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没敲就没敲嘛 我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是顺便去晃了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 这和老妈没什么关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想让你捎些点心过去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己送过去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 青春期 青春期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像话的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚参加完暑期讲习回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹我们也是重点高中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本应该穿着的…高中的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:54.75,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不说这个 你才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪集 还有鹤见子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 是芽间她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说「芽间」算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 还在说这种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没去上学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填报的志愿没考上 就读这一带垫底的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学也不去上 嘴里还念着本间芽衣子的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脑子是不是进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集是个大混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你热血个什么劲儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一提到本间芽衣子的事就像变了个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也跟他一样吗 松雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没出息的家伙 就只有长相还好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑也很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下 你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都已经变了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 变得最多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的压力…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在我身边的时候 就会让我想起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会让我想起很多不愉快的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得我心神不宁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁…碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…那个时候的夏天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在这个样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 我决定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是 「超和平Busters」!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅气!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Busters是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是「一群厉害的人」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起来保卫和平吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的和平?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪都算上 各种和平!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 仁碳就做我们的领袖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都跟在我的身后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那一天也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 仁碳你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢芽间…吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你 你在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就实话实说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超和平Busters」之间不许有秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊 说啊 说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}说啊 快说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:45.67,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}快说 快说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会喜欢这种丑八怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为她会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为芽间是个爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:17:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早就回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去妈妈那一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭要热热再吃哈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.74,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6.247\pos(1113,425)}洗洗手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.74,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6.247\pos(1127,471)}热一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.74,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6.247\pos(1155,512)}再吃哈!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.74,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6.247\pos(1183,570)}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张笑脸 一直叫我放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为 明天跟她道歉就会没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却永远都不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 门开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就关一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聪 啊～长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…有好多白头发了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧 用不着一直那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做咖喱的时候总是给姐姐一份当供品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点碍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这可是姐姐最爱吃的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都死了 还能吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的姐姐 有些方面比较迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定 她还没注意到自己已经死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己已经死了这点事…还是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是我呢 是杯子自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 快点收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 又不是我弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干净漂亮地…将和平破坏掉的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:19.20,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Busters可解作「杰出的人」，也可解作「破坏者」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉之中 都各自离去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间要吃蛋花汤 蛋花汤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…可能会去的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想拥有那一天的明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能向芽间道歉的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的压力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的阴影…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定是想向芽间道歉 所以才会制造出了她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就…!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个有点太重口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴 正是这种反差 才让人欲罢不能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 这不是仁碳吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就在这里刻上名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超」字怎么写啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 左边是个「走字旁」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「走字旁」要怎么写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 冻结在这里的时间又开始流动了

